# SWC compiler target for Next.js. Mirror of the `browserslist` field in
# package.json. Next.js 16's SWC compiler does not always honor the
# package.json field, but reliably reads .browserslistrc. Added to stop SWC
# from polyfilling ES2019-2022 features (Array.at, Array.flat, Array.flatMap,
# Object.fromEntries, Object.hasOwn, String.trimStart/End) that are natively
# supported in our target browsers.
# See docs/development/PERFORMANCE_OPTIMISATION.md and the v2.1 perf log for
# context.

